des: Our EDM station is the ultimate destination for electronic dance music lovers. With a focus on the latest releases and biggest hits from top DJs and producers. Our team of experienced DJs and producers carefully curates our station so we not only bring you the biggest hits from the festivals, but bring bring the rising stars to your attention . In addition, we offer interviews and guest mixes from some of the biggest names in the industry, providing you with an inside look into the world of EDM and the artists who are shaping its future.
